            <title>[DERBY-2609] The tests in ij7.sql are only performed in embedded mode.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2609</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The tests in ij7.sql are only performed in embedded mode. They should also be performed in client mode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
